room_title: Escape room "Boxed up" by Komnata Quest in New York
room_description: Did you miss me? My name is Jim Moriarty. I like to play with my toys and make them do whatever I want. I like to keep my toys in boxes and if they can’t solve my puzzles I blow them up. If you haven’t already guessed, yes, you are my toys. Can’t wait to play with you. This will be fun!... For me.
